Parliament, Sunday, 25 August 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Tourism together with the Portfolio Committee on Police with be hosting a consultative workshop on tourist safety on 27 August 2019 at the Old Assembly Chamber from 10h00 to 16h30.      Members of the media should note that a media briefing will be held at 13h30 at Old Assembly Chamber. ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON TOURISM, MR SUPRA MAHUMAPELO. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Modise Kabeli
